      "type": "markdown",
      "text": "__Therefore: Wherever possible, and at whatever scale possible, make changes to your local “operating system for growth” to embrace economies of place and differentiation as well as scale and standardization. Slowly change out the systems that rely too much on the latter: the codes, laws, standards, models and other elements that are taking us on an unsustainable path.__",
